   version stable 1.4.1 1.4.0 1.3.1 1.3.0 1.2.1 1.2.0 1.1.1 1.1.0
   require SDL flac fluidsynth gcc-g++ libmad libmpeg2 libpng libtheora libvorbis
  optional alsa-lib      '' --disable-alsa for Sound support
  optional nasm          '' --disable-nasm for assembly language optimizations
  optional FOTAQ_Talkie
  optional bass-cd
  optional drascula
  optional lure
  optional lure-de
  optional lure-es
  optional lure-fr
  optional lure-it
      opts --disable-debug --enable-all-engines --enable-plugins --default-dynamic 
  category game development/emulator
 attribute makej x11
    source $SOURCEFORGE_URL scummvm/scummvm/$VERSION/scummvm-$VERSION.tar.bz2
      info last 20120131
      info home http://scummvm.sourceforge.net
      desc 'virtual machine for classic point-and-click adventure games.
It is designed to run:
Simon the Sorcerer 1 and 2 from Adventure Soft;
Beneath A Steel Sky from Revolution;
Broken Sword 1 and Broken Sword 2;
Flight of the Amazon Queen;
and games based on
SCUMM (Script Creation Utility for Maniac Mansion) system from LucasArts.

Now supporting also:
"The Legend of Kyrandia: Book Two: Hand of Fate",
"The Legend of Kyrandia: Book Three: Malcolm Revenge",
"Lost in Time",
"The Bizarre Adventures of Woodruff and the Schnibble",
"Drascula: The Vampire Strikes Back".'

build(){
./configure \
 --prefix=/usr \
 $OPTS &&
make &&
make install DESTDIR=$DESTDIR
}
